{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In this game, you will take control of the policeman John Smith from the remote town of Moonriver. Together with him, you will find yourself in the epicenter of a zombie apocalypse. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2964690/extras/citymaplegend__1_.png?t=1737976324\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You'll have to battle hordes of enemies, conduct an investigation, complete various quests, and find out what exactly happened here.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2964690/extras/ezgif.com-video-to-gif-converter.gif?t=1737976324\" /></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Use transportation to explore the open world of the town of Moonriver. All vehicles behave differently, find the one that suits you.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Find an advantage in the interactive environment. Create barricades from furniture and block enemies to save ammo.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A dense atmosphere of an 80s horror movies, created by hand-drawn high-resolution 2D graphics, as well as an original soundtrack.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2964690/extras/hotel.gif?t=1737976324\" /></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A large number of different enemies on the screen. Remember: <strong>&quot;One zombie - an annoyance, three - a danger, fifteen - a natural disaster.&quot;</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You will have access to an arsenal of various weapons, which will give you the freedom to choose your strategy - eliminate the enemy quietly without attracting unnecessary attention, or create some action.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A detective story with SCI-FI elements. You will need to complete quests, 